    <briefdescription>
<para>Process for computing gravitational settling of aerosol species. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This module provides the settling process interface for the CATChem library. The interface leverages CATChem&apos;s core infrastructure for data marshaling and process management. All algorithmic calculations are performed in separate scheme modules.</para>
<para>DIAGNOSTIC INTERFACE: The compute_scheme functions support optional diagnostic parameters. When diagnostics are enabled in the configuration, these parameters are passed to capture emission/tendency data. When diagnostics are disabled, the scheme calls use the original interface without diagnostics. This approach maintains backward compatibility while providing flexible diagnostic capabilities.</para>
